===Etymology===
English from the 17th century, from a {{etyl|ML.|en}} or {{etyl|NL.|en}} {{term|lexicon|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|λεξικόν||a lexicon|tr=lexicon|lang=grc}}, neuter of {{term|λεξικός||of words|tr=lexikos|lang=grc}}, from {{term|λέξις||a saying, speech, word|tr=lexis|lang=grc}}, from {{term|λέγειν||to speak|tr=legein|lang=grc}}.

